headline: Teledyne and M Subs Announce Strategic Collaboration
summary: NORTH FALMOUTH, Mass., February 27, 2026--Teledyne Marine, a global leader in maritime unmanned underwater vehicles and marine technologies, and M Subs, a UK-based innovator in marine unmanned systems and associated autonomy, are pleased to announce the signing of a Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) to establish a strategic collaboration.
